  <summary date="2021-02-01T16:51:44Z" status="Introduced in House">Second Lieutenant Richard W. Collins III Memorial Act

This bill requires the Department of Defense to provide the death gratuity and casualty assistance to the survivors of a member of the Reserve Officers' Training Corps who received a commission but died before receiving a first duty assignment.</summary>
